{"tid":2414973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國民法典：家長擅用8歲以上子女利是錢屬違法","createTime":"2021-02-20T00:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T06:10:36.000Z","uid":36494,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8c0ab6576ba2cdb6c4d58bc638e2c496a8c4b182","tid":2414973,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T00:20:29.000Z","msg":"自從今年1月1日起實施《民法典》，列明小朋友滿8歲可以獨立運用自己的收益。而父母作為監護人，雖然可以代為管理和保護小朋友的財產，包括利是錢，但不可以隨便使用，否則可能已經犯法。<br />\n<br />\n中國政法大學教授夏吟蘭接受央視訪問時，還對小朋友給予以下建議：「那是你的錢對吧，你可以交給父母讓他們幫你保管，但是一定記住保管也只是替你保管、不能幫你花。然後同時你也可以拿你這個錢，你可以想買點甚麼小東西，那也是可以買的」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/38303/%E6%B0%91%E6%B3%95%E5%85%B8-%E5%88%A9%E6%98%AF%E5%B0%81-%E7%9C%BE%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B5%84-38303/%E3%80%90%E6%8D%8D%E8%A1%9B%E5%88%A9%E6%98%AF%E3%80%91%E6%B0%91%E6%B3%95%E5%85%B8%EF%BC%9A%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E6%93%85%E7%94%A88%E6%AD%B2%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E5%88%A9%E6%98%AF%E9%8C%A2%E5%B1%AC%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95?fbclid=IwAR2HY5KeCEemJBtJr0EdTImTSBp3-RwMGXNNQp-509s_DCvXM5042Smngc0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F38303%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2585%25B8-%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25B0%2581-%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B5%2584-38303%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%258D%258D%25E8%25A1%259B%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%2598%25AF%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2585%25B8%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%2593%2585%25E7%2594%25A88%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%258C%25A2%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%25B3%2595%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2HY5KeCEemJBtJr0EdTImTSBp3-RwMGXNNQp-509s_DCvXM5042Smngc0&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=5d3c747c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/38303/%E6%B0%91%E6%B3%95%E5%85%B8-%E5%88%A9%E6%98%AF%E5%B0%81-%E7%9C%BE%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B5%84-38303/%E3%80%90%E6%8D%8D%E8%A1%9B%E5%88%A9%E6%98%AF%E3%80%91%E6%B0%91%E6%B3%95%E5%85%B8%EF%BC%9A%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E6%93%85%E7%94%A88%E6%AD%B2%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E5%88%A9%E6%98%AF%E9%8C%A2%E5%B1%AC%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95?fbclid=IwAR2HY5KeCEemJBtJr0EdTImTSBp3-RwMGXNNQp-509s_DCvXM5042Smngc0</a>"},{"pid":"12dc98feba6a1873c0accb453a7c90e794ecdf64","tid":2414973,"uid":141151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T00:30:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">那如果小孩用利是錢胡亂買東西又怎麼辦？專家指法律規定，8歲以上小朋友如何花錢，要與他的年齡、智力及家中財務狀況等相符，如果超出範疇，就要經監護人同意，叫父母不用太擔心。<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong>驚死屋企唔夠家嘈屋閉咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a18ad4df530d337359b05dd5aca037ac4473133","tid":2414973,"uid":123848,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T00:32:32.000Z","msg":"支那開放夾埋親戚告父母侵吞利是錢"},{"pid":"18173cd97360670fec41e4fec1e0571897969c9d","tid":2414973,"uid":176313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T00:38:15.000Z","msg":"就快屙屎屙尿都要管埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b43a5f21fdd04209c5a535164ddc08974ba031","tid":2414973,"uid":339130,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T00:57:42.000Z","msg":"諗呢條例嘅人細個究竟被父母氹咗幾多利是錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f89fc47f03cf669c7c4a2bc8b58eed891890684b","tid":2414973,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T01:10:53.000Z","msg":"到實行時就係公安勸父子和解，然後沒收筆錢"},{"pid":"90e739b3bd170714eda8a938a76b46e292a9397d","tid":2414973,"uid":251433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T01:26:13.000Z","msg":"父母：幫你交家用"},{"pid":"bc0